Sun Crusher:



The Brotherhood robot was very close and he stopped abruptly and hovered in 
the air for a moment.  He looked back to the latest addition of the 
Brotherhood ranks.  "Prepare for combat.  Get your strongest weapons ready.  
We will provide cover fire for our brethren."

With that, the Brotherhood member turned back around and blasted off towards 
South Africa at full speed.
